    %h2 Seven Servers
    %p Parley is client software meant to be used with the seedbox service Seven Servers. Before you configure any further, make sure you have an account.

    %a{:href => 'http://example.com', :class => 'btn success large', :target => '_blank'} Create a Free Account Â»

.row{:style => 'margin-top:60px'}
  .columns.span4
    %h2 Configuration
    %p Once you submit this form, you won't be able to access this setup page anymore.  To access it again, delete the config.yaml file in parley's directory.
  .columns.span11.well
    %form{:action => '/', :method => 'POST'}
      .clearfix
        %label{:for => 'directory'} Root Directory
        .input
          %input{:type => :text, :name => 'directory'}
          %span.help-block 
            Where do you download your files? 
            Parley will refuse to browse above this directory. 
            Make sure your webserver can serve files from here.
      .clearfix
        %label#optionsCheckboxes Other Options
        .input
          %ul.inputs-list
            %li
              %label
                %input{:name => "follow_symlinks", :type => "checkbox", :value => "true"}/
                %span Follow symlinks? Disable for security.

  
      .actions
        %input{:type => :submit, :value => 'Configure', :class => 'btn primary'}